---
import {
  CollapsibleColumns,
  Description,
  ExternalLink,
  ImageWithCaption,
  InfoListItem,
  PageleteSection,
  SectionHeader,
} from "components";

import { A11yInfoList } from "../../helpers";

import { topics } from "../static";
const { id, title } = topics.additionals;

import image1 from "../imgs/resources-additional-1.svg";
import image2 from "../imgs/resources-additional-2.svg";
---

<PageleteSection>
  <SectionHeader id={id}>{title}</SectionHeader>

  <Description>
    Here are a few additional links that will help you to design better and more
    accessible products.
  </Description>

  <CollapsibleColumns>
    <ImageWithCaption
      imgSrc={image1.src}
      imgAlt="Image showing three items of a checklist that are all marked as checked"
      captionTitle="Accessibility Checklists"
    >
      The Not-Checklist acts as a guide to make sure you haven't missed
      anything. If you're new to accessibility, it provides a foundation - it's
      an overview of what you'll need to consider, but it won't teach you WCAG
      from front to back.

      <A11yInfoList>
        <InfoListItem>
          <ExternalLink href="https://not-checklist.intopia.digital/">
            Accessibility Not-Checklist
          </ExternalLink>
        </InfoListItem>

        <InfoListItem>
          <ExternalLink href="https://codepen.io/weboverhauls/full/zYvopYE">
            WCAG 2.1 Checklist with Filter and Links
          </ExternalLink>
        </InfoListItem>
      </A11yInfoList>
    </ImageWithCaption>

    <ImageWithCaption
      imgSrc={image2.src}
      imgAlt="Image showing a video with three options to the left of the video, the options are: captions, audio description and transcript"
      captionTitle="Web Accessibility Perspective Videos"
    >
      Accessibility is essential for people with disabilities and useful for
      all. Learn about the impact of accessibility and the benefits it provides.


      <A11yInfoList>
        <InfoListItem>
          <ExternalLink href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/perspective-videos/">
            View Videos
          </ExternalLink>
        </InfoListItem>
      </A11yInfoList>
    </ImageWithCaption>
  </CollapsibleColumns>
</PageleteSection>
